# Infrastructure

The `infrastructure/` directory contains configuration and code for deploying and managing the Zeiro platform.

## Network

The Network configuration in [infrastructure/network](mdc:infrastructure/network) includes:
- Network topology
- Routing rules
- Security groups and firewall settings

## Platform

The Platform configuration in [infrastructure/platform](mdc:infrastructure/platform) includes:
- Container orchestration
- Service deployment
- Resource allocation
- Scaling policies
